# MetaWave Innovations Homepage Visual Theme Guide (MWIHOMETHEME)

This document maps out the specific colors, gradients, layout parameters, and typography hierarchy used to build the flagship **MetaWave Innovations Homepage**.

---

## 1. Homepage Typography Architecture

The homepage uses distinct typography layers to maintain readability and strong visual hierarchy:

| Element | Font Family | Tailwinds & Weights | Visual Description / Intent |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Main Hero Header** | `Plus Jakarta Sans` | `text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight` | Bold, commanding high-tech presence with progressive word gradients. |
| **Section Titles** | `Plus Jakarta Sans` | `text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight` | Clean display titles accented by subtle sub-titles. |
| **Body / Copy paragraphs** | `Inter` | `text-xs sm:text-[14.5px] font-normal text-slate-500` | Soft off-black slate gray for modern Swiss reading ergonomics. |
| **Stat Counters & Values** | `Plus Jakarta Sans` | `text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900` | Extreme-impact numbers paired with monospaced description tags. |
| **System Labels / Badges** | `JetBrains Mono` | `text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-400` | Upper-case, widely tracked mono spacing denoting code sovereignty. |

---

## 2. Homepage Color Hierarchy

The homepage structure alternates between pure crisp whites and extremely light neutral slates to create an inviting layout rhythm:

* **Canvas Background (Page):** `#FAFBFD` (Off-white silk)
* **Canvas Background (Clean Sections):** `#FFFFFF` (Pure white for high-contrast card separation)
* **Canvas Background (Shaded/Ad Sections):** `#F8FAFC` (Slate 50 / 60)
* **Brand Prime Emerald Accent:** `#326E45` (Interactive forest emerald)
* **Text Primary Slate:** `#0F172A` (Slate 900 for dark texts)
* **Text Secondary Slate:** `#475569` (Slate 600 for descriptions)
* **Border Trim Lines:** `rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8)` (Slate 200 at 80% opacity)

---

## 3. Flagship Homepage Gradients

The homepage features several premium custom gradients:

### A. Emerald Brand Master Gradient
* **Tailwind CSS Code:** `bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 via-[#326E45] to-emerald-800`
* **Used in:**
  * Primary Action Trigger Button (Hero CTA)
  * Stat impact underline elements
  * Corporate CTA section backdrop overlays

### B. Subtle Hero Radial Spotlight Glows
* **Tailwind CSS Code:** `bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-50/40 via-transparent to-transparent`
* **Used in:** Hero section header canvas background to anchor visual balance.

### C. Live Campaign Ad Backdrop (Deep Navy Slate)
* **Tailwind CSS Code:** `bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 via-[#0E1527] to-slate-900`
* **Used in:** Interactive AdSense advertisement section placeholder banners.

### D. Glossy Card Hover Glows
* **Tailwind CSS Code:** `from-emerald-500/[0.01] to-teal-500/[0.01]` transiting to `from-emerald-500/[0.04] to-teal-500/[0.04]`
* **Used in:** Tech Stack cards to produce an elegant reactive glow during user interaction.

### E. Team Profile Card Border Reflector
* **Tailwind CSS Code:** `bg-gradient-to-r from-[#326E45]/40 via-emerald-600/30 to-[#326E45]/40`
* **Used in:** Executive card toppers to indicate active state capabilities.

