## 4. Homepage Interaction Models

* **Card Elevations:**
  * *Default:* `border-slate-200/90 shadow-[0_4px_25px_rgba(15,23,42,0.01)]`
  * *Hover Transition:* `hover:border-emerald-500/30 hover:shadow-[0_25px_50px_-12px_rgba(16,185,129,0.12),0_8px_24px_-4px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)] hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300`
* **Interactive Toggles:**
  * *Active Pill:* `text-white bg-[#326E45] shadow-xs`
  * *Inactive Pill:* `text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 bg-transparent`
